{"tid":20184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"駁眼睇覺得有半個高登出走左","createTime":"2016-12-03T08:21:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T08:58:31.000Z","uid":47356,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6195c3b31787aa7af934aacece880579c0d8c029","tid":20184,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T08:21:57.000Z","msg":"有關假扮本站前職員發表失實言論聲明 <br />\n<br />\n會員「禿伯」於2011年曾在本站討論區假扮管理員，向不知情會員套取個人資料（<a href=\"http://forum2.hkgolden.com/blog/blog.aspx?userid=1&amp;view=message&amp;blogid=7366），由於事態嚴重，本站當時曾擬報警處理，後來因其苦苦哀求並答允從此不再冒充管理員，才網開一面。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum2.hkgolden.com%2Fblog%2Fblog.aspx%3Fuserid%3D1%26view%3Dmessage%26blogid%3D7366%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E6%96%BC%E4%BA%8B%E6%85%8B%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%AC%E7%AB%99%E7%95%B6%E6%99%82%E6%9B%BE%E6%93%AC%E5%A0%B1%E8%AD%A6%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%EF%BC%8C%E5%BE%8C%E4%BE%86%E5%9B%A0%E5%85%B6%E8%8B%A6%E8%8B%A6%E5%93%80%E6%B1%82%E4%B8%A6%E7%AD%94%E5%85%81%E5%BE%9E%E6%AD%A4%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E5%86%92%E5%85%85%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%93%A1%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%8D%E7%B6%B2%E9%96%8B%E4%B8%80%E9%9D%A2%E3%80%82&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexofwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=7a82d188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://forum2.hkgolden.com/blog/blog.aspx?userid=1&amp;view=message&amp;blogid=7366），由於事態嚴重，本站當時曾擬報警處理，後來因其苦苦哀求並答允從此不再冒充管理員，才網開一面。</a> <br />\n<br />\n鑑於近日網上再有人以「禿伯」之名，聲稱曾擔任本站管理員，並發表大量不實之誹謗言論，就此事本站發表以下聲明： <br />\n<br />\n一、本公司自正式由前擁有人「Dr Jim」接手網站以來，從未以其所聲稱之公司名義聘請任何人士作管理員。如有人自稱受聘於該公司作本站之管理員，必為假冒。 <br />\n<br />\n二、對於該名人士所發表的誹謗言論，本站保留追究權利。 <br />\n<br />\n三、本站管理員絕不會以任何私人形式，包括個人帳戶PM、電郵或Facebook等向用戶索取個人資料或要求提供任何密碼。如有任何人士懷疑曾受騙，請盡快報警處理，本站全力協助，將犯人繩之於法。 <br />\n<br />\n四、坊間不少網站、App和Facebook專頁均意圖假冒本站，希望各會員切勿向任何人士透露敏感個人資料或密碼，以免遭人盜用。 <br />\n<br />\n香港高登管理員團隊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請繼續爆料</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c04c876b64b79e2005386e1d5370a059098735a6","tid":20184,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T08:23:12.000Z","msg":"已淆底"},{"pid":"aa762b97e0edcbad1876628616cf7b6ac6b5c840","tid":20184,"uid":15086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T08:24:25.000Z","msg":"點至"},{"pid":"70392f520f8a6f4c897ae94932db448b4bb42700","tid":20184,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T08:47:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點至</blockquote><br />\n我陣係睇到兩邊個最後回覆而家都係on par,<br />\n以前係around 5分鐘前後<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e248da83c9417d00aba364c2f897546836ef62ec","tid":20184,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T08:48:06.000Z","msg":"驟眼睇先岩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae5be4d550e8e78e1b15c44bbc02a466f146822","tid":20184,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T08:58:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}